<p>"We applaud BEIJING ORIENTAL YUHONG WATERPROOF TECHNOLOGY CO.,LTD. for earning the USDA Certified Biobased Product label," said Kate Lewis, USDA BioPreferred Program. "Products from BEIJING ORIENTAL YUHONG WATERPROOF TECHNOLOGY CO.,LTD. are contributing to an ever-expanding marketplace that adds value to renewable agriculture commodities, creates jobs in rural communities, and decreases our reliance on petroleum."</p>
